================================================================================
THIRD-PARTY DATA NOTICE
================================================================================

The shipped dictionary file `jpn_dict.txt` and the binary engine inputs
`kj_dict.bin` / `kj_conn.bin` are derived from Google Mozc OSS data, which
in turn derives from NAIST IPAdic and the Okinawa Public-Domain Dictionary.
Their license terms are reproduced verbatim in `dict/LICENSES.txt` and MUST
ship with any binary release that includes those files.

Mozc source code that we vendor (none today, but anticipated for future
work in tsf/third_party/) is BSD-3-Clause licensed; copying it here verbatim
or modified must preserve the upstream BSD-3 notice.

The `dict/build_dict_ipadic.py` legacy builder targets mecab-ipadic-2.7.0
which carries the same NAIST + ICOT terms covered by `dict/LICENSES.txt`.
